	      <supportDesc>
		<support>
		  <p>
		    <objectType>Memorial pillar</objectType>;
		    no dimensions are given in the original publication.
		    “The records are incised on long narrow slabs of stone,
		    and in the majority of cases the inscriptions are 
		    incised lengthwise... it is apparent that the mason
		    did not take the trouble to make [the inscribed surfaces]
		    smooth before incising the letters.”
		  </p>
		</support>
	      </supportDesc>
	      <layoutDesc>
		<layout>
		  <p>
