	  rājño <persName key="pers:Caṣṭana">cāṣṭanasa</persName> <persName key="pers:Ysāmotika">ysāmotika</persName>pu<unclear>trasa</unclear> r<unclear>ā</unclear>j<unclear>ño</unclear> <persName key="pers:Rudradāman">ru<unclear>dradāmasa</unclear></persName> <persName key="pers:Jayadāman">jayadāma</persName><lb n="2" break="no"/>putra<unclear>sa</unclear> varṣe 50 2 phaguṇabahula<unclear>sa</unclear> dvitiyaṃ vā 2
