      <div type="translation" xml:lang="eng">
	<ab>
	  In the year fifty-two, 50 ,2; on the second day of the dark half of Phālguna, va . 2, of (the reign of) the king <persName key="pers:Rudradāman">Rudradāman</persName>, son of <persName key="pers:Jayadāman">Jayadāman</persName>, (the grandson) of the king <persName key="pers:Caṣṭana">Cāṣṭana</persName>, son of <persName key="pers:Ysāmotika">Ysāmotika</persName>, (this) staff was raised (in memory) of <persName key="pers:An-Ṛṣabhadeva">Ṛṣabhadeva</persName>, son of <persName key="pers:An-Treṣṭadatta">Treṣṭadatta</persName>, by his father <persName key="pers:An-Treṣṭadatta">Treṣṭadatta</persName>, a novice of the Opaśati gotra.
	</ab>
